window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Does anyone enjoy listening about a good fight with monsters? How about a story of a girl who's cursed? Oh, wait, we've all heard stories of princesses who were cursed in one form or another. But have you ever heard a tale about someone in futuristic times being cursed with becoming the very monsters you hear about the heroes slaying? Introducing the Curse on Silver Strike!</p> <p>In this extraordinary tale, protagonist Sarsha is under a curse. And she has until said curse can complete itself to break it...or countless lives will be lost. Luckily, she's not alone. The warlock Sword and the mutant-witch-hybrid Silver Strike are with her. And they're determined to break her curse! But will they be able to break the curse in time?</p>"; 
